How to use the 6.0 generator? 

When you run, it will automatically create a folder called 
"update" within this folder "update" Download all 
update files for NOD32. 

When you execute it, automatically it will create a called folder " update ", inside this folder "update" will download all update files for Nod32.

Also it will create a called file " long.ver ", this file will serve so that the Generator remembers that files download, and to the next time when you execute it, it will not download again all the files, if not only what it is necessary to update.

Remember that the file was generador.ini setting version 
package of files to download either the 2.7 or 3.0 version. 

If for some reason want to download any files again 
only removes the file "long.ver" and the folder "update". 

To set the nod32 and use the files you download Generator 
You should see the images of configuration that come along with this file.
